{"tid":404439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉兆佳：預料中共港府等社會勢力將入校園鬥爭","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T07:15:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d7d7a60d33d29c0aa91f3f537a482cc5a30701","tid":404439,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170918/s00001/c2396fdd91a6af8323ede6c1bd50bf5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2Fc2396fdd91a6af8323ede6c1bd50bf5a.jpg&h=6b756d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國港澳研究會副會長劉兆佳表示，將來可能會有社會勢力進入校園，與「港獨」勢力鬥爭，包括中央及特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳早上出席活動時，提及大學校園出現「港獨」宣傳物品，他支持大學發聯署聲明反對「港獨」。他說，不排除是校外「港獨」分子在大學宣揚「港獨」，但明言將來可能會有社會勢力進入校園，與「港獨」勢力鬥爭，當中包括中央及特區政府，故大學校長需自行管制，保護大學自主。<br />\n<br />\n劉兆佳續稱，社會反「港獨」呼聲愈來愈大，校方須盡快處理好「港獨」問題，他估計大學校園難繼續成為港獨庇護所。<br />\n<br />\n他亦提到，即使以往特區政府及大學採取包容態度，但隨着社會形勢及氣氛變化，這種包容可能會「消失」。"},{"pid":"2b9d405a978b1f16f303f85e1d490a4401b6af6c","tid":404439,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:09:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710345994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710345994&d=dBg6tSW81F0Leg6ahdWzMaNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=2a2b00b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710345994&h=39f6fa35\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710345994</a>"},{"pid":"590451e888ea27ff3c24715c15d5f023619ece37","tid":404439,"uid":9286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:11:12.000Z","msg":"狗共要再次掀起文革 誰也擋不了"},{"pid":"ac421d1115f1264731b1c77b1e965c20ceb697e0","tid":404439,"uid":93784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit